# fastlane
#
# It is recommended to not store the screenshots in the git repo. Instead, use fastlane to re-generate the
# screenshots whenever they are needed.
# For more information about the recommended setup visit:
# https://docs.fastlane.tools/best-practices/source-control/

**/fastlane/report.xml
**/fastlane/Preview.html
**/fastlane/screenshots
**/fastlane/test_output

# Bundle artifact
*.jsbundle

# Ruby / CocoaPods
**/Pods/
/vendor/bundle/

# Temporary files created by Metro to check the health of the file watcher
.metro-health-check*

# testing
/coverage

# Tenet runtime state (volatile SQLite — human-readable artifacts under .tenet/ are tracked)
.tenet/.state/
# Tenet volatile build/run logs (journal·spec·knowledge·visuals 산출물은 계속 추적)
.tenet/*.log
.tenet/**/*.log
.tenet/*.err
.tenet/rn-config-check.json

# Agent tooling (개인 로컬 설정 — .mcp.json은 tenet MCP 로드에 필요해 공유 차원에서 추적)
.agents/
.codex/
.claude/skills/
opencode.json

# Yarn
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/sdks
!.yarn/versions

# Expo
.expo
dist/
web-build/

# Firebase 클라이언트 설정(google-services.json / GoogleService-Info.plist)은
# 클라이언트 config(하드 시크릿 아님, APK/IPA에 포함)라 빌드 재현성 위해 커밋한다.
# ⚠️ Firebase Admin 서비스계정 JSON(서버 전권 시크릿)은 절대 커밋 금지 — Render 환경변수로만.
serviceAccount*.json
firebase-adminsdk*.json
# Kakao 네이티브 앱 키 (머신별 주입, 공개 저장소 미커밋)
ios/Secrets.xcconfig
# Generated JS bundle for release APK (regenerated via npm run bundle:android)
android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.bundle
